        ==========================================================

                     Dave's Space Empire Version 2.01

                         Written by David Prothero

                Based on Ken's Space Empire by Ken Schenke

        ==========================================================


                 @{"   Introduction    " link INTRO}   @{"   Distribution    " link DISTR}
